description: Change of use from Class B1 (office) to museum and archive Class D1 (non-residential institution), together with 2 x 2 storey side extensions, external alterations including removal of rear staircase, provision of entrance and side steps and ramps, technical plant enclosures on roof and ground floor, 2 enclosed escape staircases at rear, internal alterations and reconfiguration of existing layout (Admin and Finance building)
